{"prompt": "Generate a website for a real estate brokerage. The website should be artistic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Azure Estates</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0077b6; /* A nice blue */\n            --secondary-color: #90e0ef; /* A lighter, softer blue */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #03045e; /* Darker blue for contrast */\n            --accent-color: #00b4d8;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 0.5rem 0;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x600/0077b6/ffffff?text=Dream+Home+Awaits'); /* Placeholder for a real image */\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            right: 0;\n            bottom: 0;\n            background-color: rgba(3, 4, 94, 0.6); /* Darker overlay for text readability */\n        }\n\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .hero-content p {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 0 1rem;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 3rem;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            background-color: rgba(0, 4, 94, 0.3); /* Slight transparency */\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .property-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .property-card {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .property-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .property-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .property-card-content {\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .property-card-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n        }\n\n        .property-card-content p {\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .property-card-content .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 500px;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border: none;\n            padding: 1rem 2rem;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Azure Estates</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#properties\">Properties</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Discover Your Dream Home</h2>\n            <p>Luxury properties tailored to your lifestyle.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"properties\">\n            <h2>Featured Properties</h2>\n            <div class=\"property-grid\">\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/90e0ef/000000?text=Modern+Villa\" alt=\"Modern Villa\">\n                    <div class=\"property-card-content\">\n                        <h3>Modern Waterfront Villa</h3>\n                        <p>5 Bedrooms, 4 Bathrooms</p>\n                        <p>Experience unparalleled luxury with stunning ocean views.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$2,500,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/00b4d8/000000?text=Urban+Loft\" alt=\"Urban Loft\">\n                    <div class=\"property-card-content\">\n                        <h3>Chic Urban Loft</h3>\n                        <p>2 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms</p>\n                        <p>Stylish city living in the heart of downtown.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$850,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/0077b6/000000?text=Cozy+Cottage\" alt=\"Cozy Cottage\">\n                    <div class=\"property-card-content\">\n                        <h3>Tranquil Forest Cottage</h3>\n                        <p>3 Bedrooms, 1 Bathroom</p>\n                        <p>Escape to nature in this charming, secluded cottage.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$450,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Azure Estates</h2>\n            <p>Azure Estates is dedicated to providing an exceptional real estate experience. We blend artistic vision with market expertise to help you find properties that are not just houses, but homes that inspire. Our commitment to personalized service ensures every client's journey is seamless and rewarding.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form class=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Azure Estates. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}